 significant differences in the eclipse\nspectrum of different HMXBs and also in their eclipse spectra against\nout-of-eclipse spectra.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Jun 2019 18:01:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-14"}
